sequenceDiagram
    participant DEV as VLAN 20 - DEV
    participant FW as Firewall/Roteador
    participant SRV as VLAN 30 - Servidor
    participant IOT as VLAN 40 - IoT
    participant MQTT as Broker MQTT
    participant GUEST as VLAN 50 - Visitante
    participant NET as Internet

    DEV->>FW: Solicita acesso ao servidor
    FW->>SRV: Permite serviço autorizado
    SRV-->>DEV: Resposta

    IOT->>FW: Publica dados MQTT
    FW->>MQTT: Permite porta autorizada
    MQTT-->>IOT: Confirmação

    GUEST->>FW: Tenta acessar rede interna
    FW-->>GUEST: Acesso bloqueado

    GUEST->>FW: Solicita acesso à internet
    FW->>NET: Acesso permitido
    NET-->>GUEST: Resposta
